data.description: Motivated seller. Move in ready. Beautiful 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath, 2 car garage with 1931 A/C sq.ft., two story custom built home on corner lot. New roof in 2014 and new exterior paint, updated kitchen with granite countertops and stainless appliances.  Enjoy open concept, cathedral ceilings, security system, central vac, and plantation shutters that allows lots of natural light in this comfortable home. NuTone sound system throughout. All accordion hurricane shutters. Low HOA fee includes lawn care, security system, monitoring, AT&T Uverse package which includes U200 DVR, HD and two additional SSTB. Community has large heated pool, spa, and tennis courts. Close to A rated schools and easy access to I95 & FL Turnpike.
data.whatILove: Lots of windows that allow for natural light in the home which is safely located on a corner lot in a small private gated community with 204 homes. Landscaping included in HOA. Walking distance to library, Publix, restaurants and coffee shops.
